    </prolog>
    <taskbody>
        <steps>
            <step>
                <cmd>Highlight the annotated text .<image placement="break"
                        href="http://beta.cwrc.ca/islandora/object/cwrc%3A40f1e7f1-7347-4e62-af31-7c82a9f939ed/datastream/OBJ/view"
                        id="image_nc2_5rd_lp" align="center" height="4in" width="6in"/></cmd>
            </step>
            <step>
                <cmd>Right-click on the highlighted text and choose the <cmdname>Edit Tag</cmdname>
                        option.<image placement="break"
                        href="http://beta.cwrc.ca/islandora/object/cwrc%3A1bb37020-a0aa-4693-a9dc-a011ff3367bf/datastream/OBJ/view"
                        id="image_srs_brv_tp" align="center"/></cmd>
            </step>
            <step>
                <cmd>Edit any information in the pop-up you would like and click
                        <cmdname>Save</cmdname>.</cmd>
                <info>None of the information in the pop-up is required.<image placement="break"
                        href="http://beta.cwrc.ca/islandora/object/cwrc%3A9c237543-7aa6-4d03-a0f7-559d929380d9/datastream/OBJ/view"
                        id="image_bpq_nqv_tp" align="center"/></info>
            </step>
        </steps>
        <result>The edited information will appear in the left "Entities" column. Click on the entry
            to see the information attached to that particular entity annotation. <image
                placement="break"
                href="http://beta.cwrc.ca/islandora/object/cwrc%3Abdfa3779-4d1a-4bc2-af47-b5be9b77b3be/datastream/OBJ/view"
                id="image_xyw_lxj_rp" align="center" height="4in" width="6in"/>
